## File a bug

### More Info:
I have tested this by downgrading each version. The expected behavior worked in `8.0.6` and started breaking in `8.0.7`. I have a suspicion that it is related to the PR #33622 that fixed the isssue #33605 in commit: https://github.com/dotnet/efcore/pull/33622/commits/f08ecf3474b65129e4bbd24e7cd03858cc1b3dc8


### Include your code

`PatientLocator.cs`
```C#
public abstract class PatientLocator : DomainEntity
{
   public int Discriminator { get; private set; }
   ....
}
```
`EntityTypeConfiguration.cs`
```C#
b.HasDiscriminator(p => p.Discriminator)
   .HasValue<PatientAddress>(0)
   .HasValue<PatientPhone>(1)
    .HasValue<PatientEmail>(2);

b.HasOne(p => p.Patient)
   .WithMany(p => p.Locators)
    .IsRequired()
    .OnDelete(DeleteBehavior.Cascade);
```

`Snapshot on 8.0.6`
```C#
 modelBuilder.Entity("DOH.CARS.Domain.PatientDirectory.PatientLocator", b =>
                {
                    b.Property<Guid>("Id")
                        .HasColumnType("uniqueidentifier")
                        .HasColumnName("PatientLocatorId");

                    b.Property<int>("Discriminator")
                        .HasColumnType("int");

                    b.Property<Guid>("PatientId")
                        .HasColumnType("uniqueidentifier");

                    b.Property<byte[]>("Timestamp")
                        .IsConcurrencyToken()
                        .ValueGeneratedOnAddOrUpdate()
                        .HasColumnType("rowversion");

                    b.HasKey("Id");

                    b.HasIndex("PatientId");

                    b.ToTable("PatientLocator");

                    b.HasDiscriminator<int>("Discriminator");

                    b.UseTphMappingStrategy();
                });
```
`Snapshot on 8.0.7`
```C#
            modelBuilder.Entity("DOH.CARS.Domain.PatientDirectory.PatientLocator", b =>
                {
                    b.Property<Guid>("Id")
                        .HasColumnType("uniqueidentifier")
                        .HasColumnName("PatientLocatorId");

                    b.Property<int>("Discriminator")
                        .HasColumnType("int");

                    b.Property<Guid>("PatientId")
                        .HasColumnType("uniqueidentifier");

                    b.Property<byte[]>("Timestamp")
                        .IsConcurrencyToken()
                        .ValueGeneratedOnAddOrUpdate()
                        .HasColumnType("rowversion");

                    b.HasKey("Id");

                    b.HasIndex("PatientId");

                    b.ToTable("PatientLocator");

                    b.HasDiscriminator();

                    b.UseTphMappingStrategy();
                });
```
